ygData.subject: New Zones
ygData.msgSnippet: On EQVault they had the new Producers Letter which Brad stated in about a month we ll have a new zone free to d/l and another one  a month or two after that.
ygData.messageBody:
On EQVault they had the new Producers Letter which Brad stated in about a
month we'll have a new zone free to d/l and another one a month or two
after that. I think he said theres 3 new zones getting ready to be put up.
They don't know if they want it to where you HAVE to get the new zones or a
only if you want them type of deal. You can bet I'll get them.

**************************
Azor
Lvl 18 Human Cleric of the Rathe
